headline: Wall Street banked on a flurry of deals under Trump in 2025. It wasn't that simple
summary: Dealmakers expected a flood of M&A to take place in 2025 following the election of President Trump. The number of transactions didn't live up to the hype.

headline: 2 Reasons to Watch EA and 1 to Stay Cautious
summary: Electronic Arts’s 35.4% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 22.4%, and its stock price has climbed to $203.89 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
